snippet.textDisplay:
#flattenthecurve ! cuz tho it may not directly reduce total # cases, indirectly it could!

it buys us time to study treatments (e.g. today's news about Chloroquine), produce masks, and other things that could reduce case #.

it also buys time to produce ICUs or treatments that could raise the 'dotted line' (healthcare capacity).

so it doesn't just help us keep our healthcare system below overcapacity but also could buy us time to better stop this.
